{"tid":1765013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急最後十二小時 要人填］民間記者會 第一份關於*催淚彈*嘅問卷調查","createTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T05:48:02.000Z","uid":325953,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"d657b071ea3584793239eaf56709b2c36c8a742d","tid":1765013,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jr2voOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJr2voOO.png&h=5efa2b22&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=67d8c4fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">越多人做 我地民間記者會嘅證據就越有力，但我地欠缺嘅就喺大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n需要大家幫手填！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">催淚毒煙 禍延我城<br />\nTear Gas are Poisoning Our City<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=67d8c4fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a></span><br />\n<br />\n問卷截止時間為<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">12月2日(星期一)早上10時</span></em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝大家對民間記者會嘅支持！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[size=2][blue]依家得唔多於一萬人做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624f9aedb58cdbbfd1e94b2cffd637c3b86975d1","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ae97a733685538818e75c31aa1ac557eaeb4c39","tid":1765013,"uid":325953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJH7q5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJH7q5H.jpg&h=db7cd2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一part喺分辨你身體嘅各部份受到嘅影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你喺22左前腳嘅，就需要於21-30嘅 2 格仔tick上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8f23a31ad13be05cecf22afa605c4bccecb1a6","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"推左再spread"},{"pid":"cf85865e039e34189c45245b3f89fea9d45c1543","tid":1765013,"uid":325953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"[民間記者會] <br />\n<br />\n🌫催淚毒煙問卷調查📊<br />\n<br />\n民記需要直接接觸/間接接觸過催淚煙嘅你/你嘅朋友/你嘅仔女去填今次問卷提供「本地數據」去支持我哋向公眾再次重申催淚煙嘅禍害！<br />\n<br />\n得返唔夠48小時😭做完記得叫埋身邊嘅多數派/少數派做啦！<br />\n一齊將份問卷Spread開去📈<br />\n<br />\n問卷截止時間為 12月2日(星期一)上午10時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0dVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=67d8c4fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a>"},{"pid":"44b91c18e5d09d8ec9e9b80abe8150e3a930cf30","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02356c6aec700b35ee095c9f74815f08efb4b931","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81130b3511fd674ecac1e9cd762048f2d0809813","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e9871ef9fbe17967fb73b823c79df673d03717","tid":1765013,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9400572338d430663077069134359eb7de0dddc","tid":1765013,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a1d812864292f34920e46a7e744e3ec6b894b3","tid":1765013,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b06c469f7767e71a74f3bf19a5ca51aec93fb8","tid":1765013,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0d2c5ee01